high_descs: Go to the bath tub to your right.
Pick up the soap in the bath tub.
Take the soap to the sink behind you.
Wash the soap in the sink.
Place the soap in the center of the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Place clean soap in the bath tub.

high_descs: Pick up the soap from the tub.
Bring the soap to the sink.
Wet the soap in the sink.
Bring the soap to the tub.
Put the soap in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put wet soap in the tub.

high_descs: Turn around and pick up the soap that is directly under you in the bathtub
Turn right and head to the sink
Place soap into the sink and turn on the faucet then turn off the faucet
Turn right and head to the bathtub
